{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_02_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 休息を知らない怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　休暇ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、東京に移転してからもみんな頑張って\nくれたからな。たまにはゆっくりしてほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Everyone has been working so hard since we moved to Tokyo.\nA break every now and then is good for everybody.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリに勝ってから\n一気にオファーが増えましたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that we’ve been getting a lot of offers\nsince we won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "メディアの露出も増えて、最近忙しいですから\n休みをもらえるのは嬉しいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With all the media sessions and work‚\nI guess a day off isn’t such a bad idea…but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いつもより歯切れが悪いな……\n何か不安でもあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sound a little unsure.\nAre you worried about something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……言いにくいんですけど、その\n……実は最近、自分のダンスに自信が持てないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… it’s not easy to say out loud‚ but…\nLately‚ I haven’t felt confident about my own dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirやBIG4のパフォーマンスはもちろん\n他のグループと比べても、実力不足を感じてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s LizNoir and the BIG4‚ of course‚\nbut I feel inadequate even compared to the other groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに、のんびり休んでなんていられない……\nもっと、頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just feel like this isn’t the time to take a break…\nI have to keep working harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（怜のダンスは、新人の中では飛び抜けて上手い）\n（……でも自分に厳し過ぎる。だから満足出来ないんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Rei’s dancing is head and shoulders above the other rookies.)\n(But she’s setting impossibly high expectations for herself.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（目標が高いのはいいけど）\n（こんな風に張り詰めてたままじゃ、よくない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Having big goals is all good and well‚)\n(but it’s a different matter if it leads to unnecessary stress.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私\nやっぱり休みはなしで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.\nI should not take any day off…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今日から三日間オフを取ってもらうぞ\nいや、やっぱり今の怜には休息が必要だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you’ll be taking three days off from today.\nYou need rest‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "休息するのも仕事のうちだ。怜なら分かるだろ？\n好きなことをして過ごしてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Resting is part of your job. You understand‚ don’t you‚ Rei?\nDo something that you enjoy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんがそんなに言うのなら……\n分かりました、じゃあダンスの自主練をします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you insist‚ {user}-san…\nFine. I’ll use the time to practice dancing on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、それだと普段と変わらないだろ？\nちっとも休んでないじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ that’s no different from what you usually do.\nThat’s not called taking a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "私、体を動かしてる方が落ち着くんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel more relaxed when I’m physically active.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜はストイックだ。いつか反動がくるぞ。ああ見えて\n麻奈もそういう所があったから、怜のことも心配なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too hard on yourself‚ Rei. Sooner or later‚ you’ll experience blowback.\nMana had similar qualities‚ which is why I’m concerned about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんも……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana was also like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、デビューしてから休んだことなんて\n全然なくて……。大事な場面で倒れたことがあってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. She never took time to rest after her debut.\nShe ended up fainting during an important concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "……あの麻奈さんにも\nそんなことがあったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t know even Mana\nwent through this sort of thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。心配させるつもりはありません\n私、休みます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand now. Sorry to make you worry.\nI’ll take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "気合を入れて、一生懸命休みますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll push myself to rest properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに力んだら休息にならないよ\nリラックスして、趣味でも楽しんでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won’t be able to rest if you push yourself to do it.\nJust relax and enjoy a hobby or something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "私の趣味、ダンスなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My hobby is dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それ以外に何かないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anything else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われても……星見プロに入る前から\nダンス漬けの毎日でしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know… Dancing was everything for me‚\neven before I joined Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "他の趣味なんて急には作れません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t exactly just sit down and pick up a hobby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、何か今、一番興味があることでいい\n旅行とか食べ歩きとか……何かないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there anything that you’re interested in right now?\nTraveling‚ eating out… anything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.33333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "旅行と言っても、他のメンバーは仕事ですから\n一緒に行けませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other members still have to work.\nThere’s no point in traveling on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "食べ歩きはダメです\n体形維持は、アイドルとして必須ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As an idol‚ I have to maintain my weight‚\nso eating out is out of the question as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこまで厳しく考えなくても……あ、雫みたいに\n釣りはどうだ……？　気分転換にはいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you’re overthinking things… Oh‚ what about fishing‚\nlike Shizuku? It’s a good change of pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "実は星見の寮の頃、一度だけ一緒に行ったんですけど\nエサをつけるのが……その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We went once when we were living in the Hoshimi dorms.\nBut‚ er‚ well… putting bait on the hook is‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "結局全部、雫につけてもらって、ちょっと……\n……あのうねうねしてるの、苦手です！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku ended up doing all the work‚ so…\nI just can’t get used to that squirmy feel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……。でも、ダンス以外にも\n趣味を持つのは、今後の活動のためにも大切だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… Thinking about the future‚ though‚\nit’s important to have a hobby other than dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル活動は、何年も続く持久戦でもある\n力の抜き方も知っておかなきゃ続かない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The career of an idol is a marathon.\nYou’ll burn out quickly if you don’t know how to relax once in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.32756280340254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "そのために趣味を持てと？　……分かりました\nちなみに、そっちは趣味あるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I need a hobby? …Alright.\nSpeaking of which… do you have a hobby?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "俺？　ゲームをすることはあったけど……\n最近はほとんどさわってないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me? I used to play video games in my spare time…\nBut I barely touch them these days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_01-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "お休みの時は何をしているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you do on off days?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
