      "text": "でも、趣味を見つけるのって……\nどうすればいいんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what should I do\nin order to discover a hobby?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.8333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
